snippet.title: Tank Battle/Air Battle #4 - VC 4000
snippet.description: Just going through the modes of this cartridge. The gameplay will not make any sense to you unless you also read the blog. The game only supports two players. Great sound and graphics in this game from 1978. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/01/tank-battleair-battle-4-vc-4000.html
